  "title": "Insect pests of pigeonpea in South Africa survey report",
  "abstract": "The incidence of pests in pigeon peas cultivated in South Africa was observed for the first time in surveys of field trials and plots undertaken in May 2000. The major insect pests observed were Clavigralla spp., Helicoverpa armigera and Callosobruchus spp.",
